This set of armor is decorated with motifs of prosperity, plenty, and generosity, such as helping hands, cornucopias, or flourishing plants. Once per day, when the wearer of a suit of benevolent armor performs a [[boost]] action to protect another person or otherwise help them in a time of need, gain [[advantage]] on the attempt.